<item>
            <title>[LU-3620] missing CLF_RENAME_LAST flag in CL_RENME record</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3620</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CLF_RENAME_LAST flag is supposed to be set in RENME changelog record&lt;br/&gt;
if the rename operation unlinks the target.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following reproducer shows this is not the case in lustre 2.4.0:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;touch /mnt/lustre/foo&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;touch /mnt/lustre/bar&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;mv /mnt/lustre/foo /mnt/lustre/bar&lt;br/&gt;
 mv: overwrite `/mnt/lustre/bar&apos;? yes&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lfs changelog lustre&lt;br/&gt;
 271361 01CREAT 13:28:02.446421944 2013.07.23 0x0 t=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x300000400:0x19b51:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; p=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200000007:0x1:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; foo&lt;br/&gt;
 271363 01CREAT 13:28:04.815421715 2013.07.23 0x0 t=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x300000400:0x19b52:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; p=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200000007:0x1:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; bar&lt;br/&gt;
 271365 08RENME 13:28:10.255420121 2013.07.23 0x0 t=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x300000400:0x19b52:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; p=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200000007:0x1:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; bar s=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x300000400:0x19b51:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; sp=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200000007:0x1:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; foo&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;RENME flag is 0x0, should be 0x01.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The flag was still correct on lustre 2.3.0:&lt;br/&gt;
6 08RENME 13:33:51.820025792 2013.07.23 0x1 t=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200000400:0x2:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; p=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x61ab:0x4710a859:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; bar s=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200000400:0x1:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; sp=&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x61ab:0x4710a859:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; foo&lt;/p&gt;</description>
